PMID== 1588841
TI  == effects of haemolysins of groups a and b streptococci on cardiovascular system.
AB  == anaesthetized new zealand white rabbits and rats were either injected or infused  with streptolysin s and group b streptococcal haemolysins in order to observe the haemodynamic actions of these haemolysins. results showed that streptolysin s had little or no effect. in contrast, group b streptococcal haemolysin showed significant hypotensive action as manifested in rapid reduction of systolic, mean, diastolic and pulse pressures, and a limited number of deaths due to shock.
TIHT== 
